description:
1st Date Guide from Expert Dating Coach [Insights to Female Psychology]

In this course you will learn the steps you need to have incredible first dates that will turn into second dates.

You will learn how to avoid common dating mistakes and pitfalls. You will learn best places to go and where not to go. You will learn how to lead the conversation to make your date feel that chemistry that women always talk about.
title: 1st Date Guide from Expert Dating Coach [Dating Insights]
